{"tid":2300283,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"紀律部隊算唔算大學乞食科不二之選?","createTime":"2020-11-25T11:33:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T12:15:00.000Z","uid":371092,"like":2,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"beeca29109d3221d83fe22abd21ec7429af2386b","tid":2300283,"uid":371092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T11:33:23.000Z","msg":"戴左頭盔先一定唔係狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雖然其他都唔好得去邊，但消防救護呢d起碼都係救人而唔係打人，點都值得尊重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n正題，大學畢業可以直接考主任/幫辦級，入職要求又唔算好高。<br />\n<br />\nFG人工大概33k~43k不等，even高過其他普通政府工，至少都跑贏私人市場果d濕9 FG價 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 穩穩定定頂薪可以上7萬幾8萬，升到仲有10萬幾。而且有唔少福利，起碼呢個時勢唔炒算偷笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n工作方面，海關入境果d壓力應該唔算好大，聽講有d散仔個人都係廢下廢下都又碌到入去。不過消防搵命搏係respect既<br />\n<br />\n一個大學非轉科，冇專長既fg價多數都13~18k。對於一d冇大志/唔係好上進既人黎講，海關入境消防呢d係咪真係一份順工?"},{"pid":"208fa84a43708f00984683354ad4c86c5beda268","tid":2300283,"uid":108337,"like":33,"dislike":2,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T11:34:24.000Z","msg":"咪即係唔同品種既狗"},{"pid":"0ba8d452a136626df4ad9cb4a60839a684c26ead","tid":2300283,"uid":118754,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T11:35:05.000Z","msg":"大家都係狗<br />\n何必分得那麼細"},{"pid":"61a81790308d6aa3eae840c0f9b2f3da83c9d655","tid":2300283,"uid":39215,"like":16,"dislike":23,"score":-7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T11:36:10.000Z","msg":"係 不過唔好以為好易考<br />\nOfficer 級要精英中既精英<br />\n入境 海關散仔一早請夠哂人<br />\n好難爭"},{"pid":"0ebce005ec70a75a84634c61a23f14b8e6f34870","tid":2300283,"uid":371092,"like":2,"dislike":15,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"208fa84a43708f00984683354ad4c86c5beda268","tid":2300283,"uid":108337,"like":33,"dislike":2,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T11:34:24.000Z","msg":"咪即係唔同品種既狗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T11:55:32.000Z","m